    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting a rare opportunity for a buyer seeking a showroom-quality car. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine and no chips or scratches, while the interior remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing zero wear on the leather or controls. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and no performance issues. You can expect a driving experience that feels as though the car just rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 49500.0,
